    <link rel="stylesheet" href="https://maxcdn.bootstrapcdn.com/bootstrap/3.3.7/css/bootstrap.min.css">
    <script src="https://ajax.googleapis.com/ajax/libs/jquery/3.3.1/jquery.min.js"></script>
    <script src="https://maxcdn.bootstrapcdn.com/bootstrap/3.3.7/js/bootstrap.min.js"></script>
	
	<script type="text/javascript">
		$(document).ready(function(){
			$("#mail").click(function(){
				$.post("/sendmail").done(function(data){
					alert("you send a mail successfully!");
				});
			});
		});
	</script>
</head>
<body>
	<header>
		<nav class="navbar navbar-default navbar-fixed-top text-center">
			<ul class="nav navbar-nav navbar-left">
				<li><a href="/">首頁</a></li>
				<li><a href="/questionnaire">開始客製化</a></li>
				<li><a href="/product">商城</a></li>
				<li><a href="/cart">購物車 <span id="productLength"><% if (productLength) {%><%=productLength%><%}%></span></a></li>				
			</ul>
			<ul class="nav navbar-nav navbar-right">
				<li><a href="#">Library</a></li>
				<li><a href="#">關於我們</a></li>
				<li><a href="/usercenter"><span class="glyphicon glyphicon-user"></span>會員中心</a></li>
				<% if (username) { %>
					<li><a href="/">welcome back, <%= username %> !</a></li>
					<li><a href="/logout"><span class="glyphicon glyphicon-log-in"></span>登出</a></li>
				<% } else { %>
					<li><a href="/login"><span class="glyphicon glyphicon-log-in"></span>login</a></li>
				<% } %>
			</ul>
		</nav>		
	</header>
	<container>
		<div class="text-center container-top container-block">
			<h1>您的貓咪是獨一無二的，我們也是。</h1>
			<h4>為您的貓咪量身訂製健康又美味的飼料</h4>
			<h4>吃對的飼料，也要吃對的量</h4>
			<a href="/questionnaire">let's start</a>
		</div>
		<div class="text-center container-block">
			<h3>IT'S SIMPLE</h3>
			<div class="col-lg-4 container-step">
				<h3>tell us about</h3>
			</div>
			<div class="col-lg-4 container-step">
				<h3>our recommend</h3>
			</div>
			<div class="col-lg-4 container-step">
				<h3>package arrive</h3>
			</div>
			<h5> </h5>
		</div>
		<div class="container-block">
			<div>
				<div class="col-lg-6 text-center">
					<img src="images/index/1.jpg">
				</div>
				<div class="col-lg-6 text-center container-special-inner">
					<h3>誠實的建議</h3>
					<h4>卡卡貓醫療系統無銷售業績等壓力，以最老實、無偏見的呈現出最適合的飼料</h4>
				</div>
			</div>
			<div>
				<div class="col-lg-6 text-center container-special-inner">
					<h3>集合了國內外學術期刊與論文</h3>
					<h4>卡卡貓醫療系統整合國內外學界、研究單位、以及業界最新的寵物各項資訊，給您最正確，最完善的寵物飲食菜單。</h4>
				</div>
				<div class="col-lg-6 text-center">
					<img src="images/index/2.jpg">
				</div>
			</div>
			<div>
				<div class="col-lg-6 text-center">
					<img src="images/index/3.jpg">
				</div>
				<div class="col-lg-6 text-center container-special-inner">
					<h3>農委會產品把關</h3>
					<h4>你知道任何飼料上架前都需經農委會的審核嗎？卡卡貓幫您將所有未經核准或有不良紀錄之廠商自動移除。</h4>
				</div>
			</div>
			<div>
				<div class="col-lg-6 text-center container-special-inner">
					<h3>安心紀錄身體狀況</h3>
					<h4>貓咪對環境及飲食過敏產生反應固然是飼主最頭痛的問題之一。透過卡卡門智慧演算，我們陪您一步一步了解貓咪的過敏原，找出您最適飼料。</h4>
				</div>
				<div class="col-lg-6 text-center">
					<img src="images/index/4.jpg">
				</div>
			</div>
			<div>
				<div class="col-lg-6 text-center">
					<img src="images/index/5.jpg">
				</div>
				<div class="col-lg-6 text-center container-special-inner">
					<h3>獸醫醫療認證</h3>
					<h4>卡卡貓除有獸醫學界的專業顧問，更定期的與醫界更新伴侶動物醫學知識，確保每位飼主家裡的喵寶吃到最安心的選擇。</h4>
				</div>
			</div>
		</div>
		<footer>
			<div class="col-lg-12 text-center">
				<h3>Here put some info about team</h3>
				<p>CATCATMEDINFO</p>
				<% if(username) { %>
					<a href="#" id="mail">click here to send testing email</a>
				<% } %>
			</div>		
		</footer>
	</container>	
</body>
</html>